    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Master Engine (GME) is a virtual tabletop built to run accessible, readable 3D battles and encounters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed for Game Masters who want combat to flow smoothly, GME makes distance, height, and positioning instantly clear, so combat flows smoothly without breaking immersion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use GME to build:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tactical combat encounters</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dungeon rooms and boss fights</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vertical battles with ledges, cliffs, and elevation</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One-shot adventures</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With an intuitive drag-and-drop interface and over +3,500 props, creating encounters is quick and flexible, even if you’re new to virtual tabletops.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are <strong>no subscriptions</strong> and <strong>no hidden costs</strong>. Buy once and use it at your own pace. GME is actively developed and continues to grow beyond just encounters, but today, it excels at making battles clearer, faster, and more enjoyable for everyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tactical Combat Encounters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451680/extras/a62e4d57b9bce091e2e0de442b37c3a6.poster.avif?t=1769478411\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as